  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>数字生命卡兹克</span> <span>2025-09-16 09:31</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">北京</span></p>\n  <p>抽象又魔幻</p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=59fb3976&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURq4Tcuu7xNCmIIalubdgG7lrPl9uTscxyeNIxooMuFdRappfNrGBXfHFdBhpwosFiatEwQiaeCYjZcQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个世界，终于魔幻到我看不懂的程度了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">故事是这样的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我最近刷淘宝挺多，然后昨天，鬼使神差的，在淘宝上，搜了一下DeepSeek。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">没有特定的理由，就是心血来潮，就是单纯的，想看看现在的生态。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后，随手点开了一家店，就是这个。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500191443\" data-ratio=\"0.37286821705426354\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1290\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d87c1605&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURq4Tcuu7xNCmIIalubdgG7l0fz3aB8hWFXiavbARA7T1eB52EF3eYuhmEFy1kxjXRhDickxmUVER4Cg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">原因很简单，以为它说无需部署，打开即用，还不卡顿。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">卖10块钱，已经有1000人付过款了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我寻思了一下我没寻思明白，又不需要买家本地部署，还能保证立刻响应，这是什么神仙办法？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">要知道别看DeepSeek的风，已经过去半年了，但是现在，你有时候还是有可能会见着这个可能会让你PTSD的玩意的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191444\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3070652173913043\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"368\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"368\" data-backh=\"113\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c9563391&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURq4Tcuu7xNCmIIalubdgG7lmrnKCCMjGSyQmIRtMTFiaJyqUwEiakZX6eogic9kpZkqibo6biaibPibRIIKg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">于是我就点进去了，这数据还确实挺好的，DeepSeek的需求还是旺。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191445\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6519379844961241\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1290\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d467222a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURq4Tcuu7xNCmIIalubdgG7lXYIqkHj9oamu8x4a1cIrTrfwyrjeiaLOD6jdHY0kr4cmnQL6FzhnjHA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">手机版9.9，电脑版9.9，两个你还在一起买，可以便宜1块钱，18.9。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191453\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.245736434108527\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1290\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f8769266&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURq4Tcuu7xNCmIIalubdgG7lUDvRsSZZeN3OdSacVPiayPBrBt23vYxKibgu1GTf3g8U6DRbrnjSLwaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">于是，我就下了单，付了款。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后，对方给我发的东西，我差点以为我特么进平行宇宙了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191446\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.163265306122449\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1078\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6f97c713&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURq4Tcuu7xNCmIIalubdgG7lsqsqHKLcrWZvIQ3iahzjHqqtkDXmHMTIvGfYhgiavBBFAzN84G8JOO8A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">给我发了两个网址。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我第一反应，这是什么菩萨，居然自己部了DeepSeek开了公网给大家用？算力这么足？不是有这资源哥们你直接去卖算力多好啊啊？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后，我定睛一看，哎？不是，这网址我怎么感觉似曾相识？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">n.cn？？？？？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这不是...360的纳米搜索？？？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191447\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5990740740740741\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=773a4121&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURq4Tcuu7xNCmIIalubdgG7lwgKub22nfA8SyMfS4RnqFw9Lc3WLPafwRCU7QIAX0j926mzSM84G4A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我点开另一个网址。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191449\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5612608032536858\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1967\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6c7e842f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURq4Tcuu7xNCmIIalubdgG7lTojjQyhOOSO9K9PhOxqM33RTh9U85icuGbjia5fNq96XI7lQCJH5dFzA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我一时间无语凝噎，我的大脑宕机了整整10秒钟。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我想到了这个事情比较抽象，但是，我没想到能抽象到这种地步。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我可能，发出了我这辈子，也是最抽象的一条回复。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我说：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">这两个我都有了。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191450\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.18070175438596492\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"570\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=82996b48&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURq4Tcuu7xNCmIIalubdgG7lpLeARfwicNic4JVnd9Fmd3zhaiaonV0Jz4oBu7urwhB3yhy2pTMGicbSYw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后，对方，又给我发了一个，说，再附送一个你没有的智能产品。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191451\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5487804878048781\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"574\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9555ca95&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURq4Tcuu7xNCmIIalubdgG7lfI3zGu6XfaLC7WQGW3Qiaa3UZy5Gxy3pKx8w6icgvtddo3q8WF60L3qA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">K...I...M...I。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">不是哥们，我寻思Kimi也没接DeepSeek啊。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">然后他又发了我飞书链接，里面有一些其他的客户端。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">我颤颤巍巍的回了一句：我也都有了。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191454\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.789103690685413\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"569\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"569\" data-backh=\"449\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=79bd1ce4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURq4Tcuu7xNCmIIalubdgG7ld2t0NDqyhxZa1jKGsZpbaIcPmojuxnRzL4GXAHUCnavh9TeedWTFzA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">哥们非常的震惊，来了一句：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">Kimi你也有了？？？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">几个链接，9.9。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我饱含着Resepect，颤颤巍巍的打开了这个产品的评论区。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为，反差感极强，我本来会以为，哥们就卖链接，肯定不少差评，但，事情不太一样了起来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个评论区，几乎全是好评。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191452\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.42777777777777776\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ebf07472&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURq4Tcuu7xNCmIIalubdgG7lsQqSNviacAYdIehv4x4MNlFAyy7j60QxlibHnOKF6p0xxxXRv08lefwQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">甚至有300个88VIP的好评。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我一条一条的看了下去，我感觉，这个世界在我的脑中，好像更魔幻，更立体了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">有用户留言说，确实不卡，输出的代码很规范。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191455\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7333333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1290\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2c3d97f8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURq4Tcuu7xNCmIIalubdgG7l9kAibW9yka70icFicyWKRzdXR6t1nULPHdfEDticUPia2JU1NGzXTpXlueQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也有人说。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191456\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.073643410852713\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1290\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=575941f2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURq4Tcuu7xNCmIIalubdgG7lvlDpWUYT1VJ9iaPfVv8T1lUtXXn5CDYqTAEmY84gg4n0KuGoxvsO51w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还有用户说，企业专线就是快。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191457\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6573643410852713\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1290\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ec84a4e1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURq4Tcuu7xNCmIIalubdgG7l5iclS7SjIJr3qId2b3HOQjvkIlBl44IAPGtpEpag3MMJ0EIiaSA90X3A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">虽然我也不理解，这玩意企业专线在哪。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">哦360自己接的模型，确实是企业专线。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后还有最让我觉得无奈的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191458\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.63203125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ec6ebd37&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURq4Tcuu7xNCmIIalubdgG7lqKWuA9xxA7eFZWy6b6USS4CCdMTXQ1mTIsgGwyKEALzaal4G0k68dw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">可以啊，是免费的r1，跟描述一致，性价比很高，不用买会员了也。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不用买会员了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我不知道你们是什么感受，我突然鼻子一酸。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我看到的，忽然是一个个非常活生生、立体形象的人。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他可能是一个刚毕业的学生，在某个四五线城市，找了一份没什么薪资不算满意但必须糊口的工作。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">白天被老板Pua，晚上回到十几平米的出租屋，想学点新东西改变命运。他听说了AI，听说了大模型，听说了这个时代最激动人心的技术革命，他觉得自己不能再被落下了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他到处找，到处试，看到的是各种需要魔法上网的官网，是动辄几十上百块一个月的会员订阅，是充满了复杂术语和技术门槛的部署教程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他找到了DeepSeek和ChatGPT的网站，付了闪闪发光的会员，好贵，而且还很卡，为什么到处都需要钱。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还不知道为什么，历史记录里总是会出现一些莫名其妙的不是他问下的记录。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他一次次尝试，一次次被碰上墙壁停滞不前，那种感觉，就像整个时代的列车都在呼啸而过，而他连站台的入口都找不到。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后，他在淘宝上看到了这个9.9元的宝贝，标题写着“无需部署”、“打开即用”、“立刻响应”，这几个词，对于他来说，就是福音。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他犹豫了很久，怕又遇到骗子，他决定用两顿拼好饭的钱，下了单，然后收到了几个可以直接点开的链接。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他试了一下，真的能用，而且很流畅。那一刻，他一定长舒了一口气，感觉自己终于花最少的钱，拿到了通往新世界的船票。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他心满意足地打开评论区，打下了那句“性价比很高，不用买会员了也”。他甚至可能觉得自己占了天大的便宜，用9.9元的价格，撬动了原本需要昂贵会员才能享受的生产力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他把这个链接，小心翼翼地收藏在了浏览器的书签里，把它当成自己在这个残酷世界里，发现的一个小小捷径和宝藏。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他不知道，这个宝藏，其实就散落在阳光下，对所有人免费开放。他只是，恰好站在信息的阴影里。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们以为我们生活在同一个时代，但好像，我们可能生活在被折叠起来的不同空间里。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">有一本我很喜欢的书，叫《北京折叠》。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191459\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1984375\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width: 578px;height: 693px;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OjgKEXmLURq4Tcuu7xNCmIIalubdgG7lGluqUjPyjFcv5EnzLVTSzibpRcCEO6mHp6yXssviaOVC91o04MWcqXBw/0?wx_fmt=other&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1844\" data-cropy1=\"867.7647058823529\" data-cropy2=\"3078.650519031142\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=89362b55&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURq4Tcuu7xNCmIIalubdgG7lEFdSuc3viaj8zGWlLhXszPiaMBvL73sNQhfibjBENqmGVWJXj334hGzFw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这篇小说里，</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">北京被分成了三个物理空间，不同阶层的人，生活在不同的空间里，共享着同一个24小时。他们彼此看不见，彼此不理解，生活在同一个城市，却像是隔着一个宇宙。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而在AI时代，在信息泛滥的今天，好像，我们进入了信息折叠。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">第一空间里的人，是信息的创造者和定义者。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他们用着最新的模型，追着最新的论文，享受着技术带来的最大红利。他们知道Kimi的母公司叫月之暗面的，知道Gemini超过ChatGPT是以为Banana，知道DeepSeek的R2至今还没有发。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对他们来说，这些都是常识，就像呼吸一样自然。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">第二空间里的人，是信息的追随者和消费者。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他们可能不知道这些工具的具体背景，但他们知道去哪里找到它们。但他们会刷科技的公众号，会看B站的科普视频，他们有能力，也有渠道，去辨别和获取免费、优质的信息。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他们看到这个9.9元的链接，可能会会心一笑，感叹一句，信息差真是门好生意。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">而第三空间里的人，是信息的隔绝者。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他们被巨大的信息噪音和高耸的技术壁垒，挡在了门外。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他们知道AI很好，很强大，但他们不知道如何触及。他们面对的，是一个需要付费、需要会员、需要辨别真伪的，复杂而充满陷阱的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">黑暗森林。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个非常抽象的转发一下链接的生意，、</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">之所以能成立，并且销量过千，恰恰说明了这道信息的鸿沟，有多么深，多么宽。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们总以为赛博朋克是霓虹灯、是飞行汽车、是义体改造。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但赛博朋克的核心，从来都是</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">“High Tech, Low Life”</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">顶尖的科技，和底层的生活。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI本应是那把能捅破所有信息壁垒的利刃，但它现在，却讽刺地，成为了壁垒本身。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我忽然想到了我的父亲。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他今年快六十了，是个非常努力想要跟上时代的人。前段时间，他看新闻说AI可以修复老照片，特别兴奋，翻出了很多爷爷奶奶年轻时的黑白照片，想让我帮他弄。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我当时随口就说，“爸，很简单啊，你下个美图APP，或者用小程序就行了。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后，我就再也没管过这件事。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">过了3个月回家，他笑呵呵的拿出手机，跟我说，我好像没弄明白，你帮我弄一下吧。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">那时候我才意识到，我一句轻飘飘的很简单，对他来说，就是一道道无法逾越的难关。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们这些自诩为懂王的人，有时候，总是轻易地嘲笑他们傻，说“这都不知道”。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">但我们忘了，我们所谓的“知道”，很多时候，只是一种幸运，而不是一种能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">我们幸运地，站在了信息流动更顺畅的地方。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而那些我们看不见的人，他们也在用自己的方式，笨拙地、努力地，想要拥抱这个日新月异的世界。他们可能走了很多弯路，花了一些冤枉钱，但他们那份向上的、不想被时代抛弃的心，是滚烫的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我会想起，在那1000多个已付款的数字背后，是1000多个具体的、努力生活的普通人。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI的发展，不会停止。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它会越来越快，越来越强，把世界甩得越来越远。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而那道信息的鸿沟，如果我们不去主动填平它，它就只会越来越深。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我会想起，在那1000多个已付款的数字背后，是1000多个具体的、努力生活的普通人。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">啰啰嗦嗦，叨逼叨了很多的废话。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也谢谢大家看到这里。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最后，用小声比比前两天，给我的一条朋友圈的评论，作为结尾吧。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比比说：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191461\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.17880794701986755\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"453\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"453\" data-backh=\"81\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fb76c1a7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURq4Tcuu7xNCmIIalubdgG7l2lZ6JPEHWusqQza6Nibhqs2mDz8nwWoXd26pxjXnUArtJFzC1h34xng%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我没什么其他的力量。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">磨平一些信息差。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这好像，就是我为数不多能做的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最棒的使命。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:var(--articleFontsize);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><strong style=\"white-space-collapse:preserve;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\">以上，既然看到这里了，如果觉得不错，随手点个赞、在看、转发三连吧，如果想第一时间收到推送，也可以给我个星标⭐～谢谢你看我的文章，我们，下次再见。</span></span></strong></strong></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"text-wrap:wrap;outline:0px;color:rgb(178, 178, 178);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:12px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-style:solid;text-decoration-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 作者：卡兹克</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 投稿或爆料，请联系邮箱：</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">wzglyay@virxact.com</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章通过淘宝上 9.9 元售卖免费 AI 链接的现象，揭示了 AI 时代下深刻的信息鸿沟和社会分层问题。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章通过淘宝上 9.9 元售卖免费 AI 链接的现象，揭示了 AI 时代下深刻的信息鸿沟和社会分层问题。",
  "summary": "作者亲身经历在淘宝以 9.9 元购买“DeepSeek”产品，却发现卖家提供的是 360 AI、Kimi 等免费大模型的公开链接。这一魔幻现象，加上商品销量过千且好评如潮（用户称“性价比高，不用买会员”），引发作者深刻反思。文章由此引申出 AI 时代下“信息折叠”的社会现实，将用户划分为信息的创造者、追随者和隔绝者三个空间。作者通过自身购买经历和与父亲关于 AI 修复老照片的对话，生动展现了底层用户在信息鸿沟中笨拙而努力地拥抱新技术的真挚愿望。文章指出，AI 本应是打破信息壁垒的利刃，却讽刺地成为了新的壁垒，形成了“High Tech， Low Life”的赛博朋克图景。最终，文章呼吁关注因信息鸿沟而被时代抛下的人们，强调填平信息差的社会责任。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "淘宝上免费 AI 链接的付费销售现象揭示了深刻的信息鸿沟。",
      "explanation": "大量用户因缺乏信息和技术认知，宁愿支付小额费用获取本可免费使用的 AI 服务，凸显了不同群体间的信息不对称。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 时代导致信息“折叠”，形成不同阶层的信息获取与理解差异。",
      "explanation": "文章将用户分为信息创造者、追随者和隔绝者三类，指出 AI 技术加剧了信息不对称，使得部分人难以触及前沿科技。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 技术在促进发展的同时，也讽刺性地成为新的信息壁垒。",
      "explanation": "尽管 AI 潜力巨大，但其高门槛和复杂性反而阻碍了底层用户接触，加剧了“High Tech， Low Life”的社会现实。"
    },
    {
      "point": "填平信息鸿沟是技术从业者和媒体的社会责任。",
      "explanation": "作者呼吁关注被信息隔绝的普通人，通过主动传播和简化信息，帮助他们拥抱新技术，共享时代红利。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "这个世界，终于魔幻到我看不懂的程度了。",
    "我们以为我们生活在同一个时代，但好像，我们可能生活在被折叠起来的不同空间里。",
    "AI 本应是那把能捅破所有信息壁垒的利刃，但它现在，却讽刺地，成为了壁垒本身。",
    "我们所谓的'知道'，很多时候，只是一种幸运，而不是一种能力。",
    "磨平一些信息差。这好像，就是我为数不多能做的。最棒的使命。"
  ],
